ch.dermitza.securenio.util

Class PropertiesReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.dermitza.securenio.util.PropertiesReader

  • public class PropertiesReader
extends java.lang.Object
    A static helper implementation for setting up static runtime options. The options are located in a Properties file. For further information on the options set, please look at the supplied setup.properties.
    Since:
    0.19
